    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. Hemolysis index prediction error of 8.3% NRMSE is within the acceptance band for worst-case operating-point identification in a Class II CPB device. The assessment team concludes that the CFD model has sufficient credibility to support the intended regulatory submission for pre-market notification of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump.",
